ZH: 他们在茶馆儿里边喝茶聊天。
EN: They drink tea and chat in the teahouse.

ZH: 昨天我去了一家很有名的茶馆儿。
EN: Yesterday I went to a very famous teahouse.

ZH: 茶馆儿里的绿茶味道很好。
EN: The green tea at the teahouse tastes great.

ZH: 老人们常常在茶馆儿里下棋。
EN: The elderly often play chess in the teahouse.

ZH: 我们下午会去附近的茶馆儿喝茶。
EN: We will go to a nearby teahouse for tea in the afternoon.

ZH: 她每天下午都会去茶馆儿看书。
EN: She goes to the teahouse to read books every afternoon.

ZH: 这个茶馆儿的环境非常安静。
EN: The atmosphere in this teahouse is very quiet.

ZH: 他们在茶馆儿里点了一壶普洱茶。
EN: They ordered a pot of puer tea in the teahouse.

ZH: 喝茶馆儿的绿茶有益健康。
EN: Drinking green tea at the teahouse is good for health.

ZH: 这家茶馆儿的装修风格很有中国传统元素。
EN: The decoration style of this teahouse has a lot of traditional Chinese elements.

ZH: 我们在茶馆儿里聊了很多很多。
EN: We chatted a lot in the teahouse.

ZH: 他们在茶馆儿里举办了一场文艺表演。
EN: They held a literary performance in the teahouse.

ZH: 茶馆儿里有很多不同种类的茶可以选择。
EN: There are many different types of tea to choose from in the teahouse.

ZH: 她在茶馆儿里遇见了一位老朋友。
EN: She met an old friend in the teahouse.

ZH: 茶馆儿的老板很热情。
EN: The owner of the teahouse is very hospitable.

ZH: 我在这家茶馆儿里品尝到了一种独特的茶。
EN: I tasted a unique type of tea in this teahouse.

ZH: 茶馆儿的服务员态度非常好。
EN: The waiter in the teahouse has a very good attitude.

ZH: 这是一家有很多历史的老茶馆儿。
EN: This is an old teahouse with a lot of history.

ZH: 茶馆儿里的茶点也非常有名。
EN: The tea snacks in the teahouse are also very famous.
